<!-- Transition ROI Deep Dive -->
<section class="py-section-gap px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop bg-on-surface text-surface relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-5 pointer-events-none">
<svg class="w-full h-full" preserveaspectratio="none" viewbox="0 0 100 100">
<path d="M0 100 C 20 0, 50 0, 100 100" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="0.1"></path>
</svg>
</div>
<div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto relative z-10">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
<div>
<h2 class="font-headline-xl text-surface mb-8">Transition ROI Deep Dive</h2>
<p class="font-body-lg text-surface-variant mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                        Moving into a strategic leadership or specialized technical role isn't just about the next paycheck. It's about fundamental capital allocation for your lifetime earning potential.
                    </p>
<div class="space-y-6">
<div class="flex gap-6 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface/10 border border-surface/20">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-4xl">payments</span>
<div>
<h4 class="font-label-md text-surface mb-1">Immediate Uplift</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-surface-variant">Average client sees a 22% increase in base salary within the first 6 months post-program completion.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-6 p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface/10 border border-surface/20">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-4xl">history_edu</span>
